name: Copy of Medical Facilitator AI Demo
description:
An interactive demo to upload medical documents (as text) and X-ray images. The app uses two AI agents to interpret the data, generate a final report, and simulate saving it to a cloud bucket.Data retriver agent handles PDF extraction

X-ray interpretation

Medical pdf analysis(pre diagnosis info)

Multimodal capability
Medical Facilitator Agent

Clinical reasoning

Treatment plan generation

Travel & logistics

Patient advocacy

finally a post diagnosis report with all findings should be reported
